{
  "id": "RAW_58619724",
  "title": "别被“多模态”骗了：用一本 200 页的教材，我测出了 GPT-5.2 和 Gemini 的物种代差",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247499989&idx=1&sn=ea6543af1cd8266486800ff2ec342f7c",
  "date": "2025-12-14 03:55:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #fff !important;padding: 40px 12px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding: 20px 24px 20px 20px;background-color: #f5f5f5 !important;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;color: #1a1a1a !important;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;border-radius: 4px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的多模态，不是给盲人装义眼，而是让他睁开眼睛。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多朋友知道，我是个“暴力测试”爱好者。之前我因为跑 Claude Code 跑得太狠，一度被官方限流。对我来说，AI 工具不是用来聊天的，是用来</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">干活</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的，而且是干</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">重活</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近在开发一个新功能时，我遇到了一个极端的“多模态”场景。这个场景，彻底暴露了目前市面上大模型的两条技术路线之争。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单说：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Pro 赢麻了，而 GPT-5.2 还停留在上个时代。</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个让 LLM 崩溃的“真”需求</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景是这样的：我手头有一本</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">扫描版教材</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（数百页 PDF，全图无文字层）和一套包含&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">200道题</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的卷子（填空、选择、简答，带图表）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的要求非常严苛：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">“模型必须只依据这本教材的内容，依次回答这200道题。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016330\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38796296296296295\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df1f5fff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCwhbuZ7BvgzZzNqDPh8xsEYdgvJibxTrDicPsrnJa57q24MpuuHPLhj3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不仅是考逻辑，更是考“眼力”和“脑回路”。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-5.2：勤奋的“胶水工程师”</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我先把任务丢给了 GPT-5.2（以及目前的 Claude Opus 4.5）。如果你懂技术原理，你盯着它的思考过程，会觉得既好笑又心酸。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-5.2 实际上是在“作弊”。它根本“看不懂”这几百页的像素。它的处理逻辑是典型的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Pipeline思维</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它发现是扫描件，慌了。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">调用 Python Sandbox。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">引入 OCR 库（文字识别），开始疯狂地把图片转成文字。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">把识别出来的、支离破碎的文本塞进 Context Window。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后才开始做题。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">代价是什么？</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">时间：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;以前我讲过“时间就是金钱”，这次它足足跑了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">20多分钟</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，才只出来前面16道题的答案。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，好在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">回答的质量还是不错的</span>，准确率100%。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不叫多模态，这叫&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">“胶水多模态”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。它是在用上个时代的 OCR 技术，给盲人 LLM 强行装了一副义眼。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从图中可以看到GPT-5.2的挣扎：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它在任劳任怨、勤勤恳恳地写代码、做OCR文字识别</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不偷懒，跑了20分钟也还没放弃，出现了前16道题的答案。（但是我们有200道题啊）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我要求“一次性输出全部”时，它继续跑了67多分钟了，也还没放弃，而我准确放弃等它了</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016331\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a76a88a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCXq2FwpunicibMT8b5H0wPsdUDhLVB4oc0TIKLhkCHu6loUXxMXQymp9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016340\" data-ratio=\"0.6324074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30a6282b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCx8cva33LX3BpcVPAD7JTGaKNuN1nt0m7QQ1ND6GlFdcqWcXmmKFluQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Pro：原生的力量</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样的 Prompt，同样的文件，我丢给了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Pro</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有代码解释器。没有 OCR 进度条。没有中间商赚差价。它直接“看”了进去。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果：1分钟。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">全部 200 道题，各种题型都答案完美输出，连教材第几页的图表细节都引用得清清楚楚。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有一丝丝的挣扎和费劲。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">答案仍然是100%准确</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016333\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf386861&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCNgc2Pe7VcfxiaRukuriajCgaBVQjLNMpcrpz6n9ag18DyyJicx9WibGb3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016334\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b40b8334&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCe0NHf7g8CRDG7tIgaK93hFAfLtJzEIUib82pW0Rr2FHjZeqMzLUnIzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016335\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f0072dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCZTrUe2ryZOX7XObcaEEs6KIEVKLI5xJSSfxwa7KSOvNRqVmialjZicaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我甚至顺手让Gemini 3 Pro做成了PPT，每页一道题，如果用户打错了，给出正确答案、再从教材找出正确答案的依据。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016336\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6888888888888889\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2805c48f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCYOgBEONyU0WXX2oY1hK8qWPuQFuaRVzByx3amibqBKCKxCODGeHFPjw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">视网膜 vs 抄写员：本质的区别</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么差距这么大？这就好比我们人类看书。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你翻开一本扫描版教材时，你的视网膜会给大脑报警说：“</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">等等！这是像素图片，不是矢量文字，我无法阅读！</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">” 吗？当然不会。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在人类（以及 Gemini 3 Pro）眼里，信息的本质是</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">光</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。不管它是印刷出来的字，还是屏幕上的截图，甚至是手写的草稿，只要“光”进了眼睛，大脑就能秒懂。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 GPT-5.2 的处理方式，就像是一个</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">极度死板的抄写员</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。他看到图片的反应是：“这不合规！我只认识 TXT 文本！” 于是他不得不先把图片拿去复印、扫描、转录成纯文本，确认没有乱码了，才肯开始读。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 是长了眼睛的，而 GPT 只是手里拿了个扫描仪。</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">信息熵的丢失</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为一个做产品的人，我还想从更底层的角度聊聊。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-5.2 这种“OCR + LLM”的胶水模式，最大的问题其实不是慢，而是</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">信息熵的剧烈丢失</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一张图片包含的信息量是巨大的：文字的大小暗示了重要性，图表的颜色暗示了趋势，段落的布局暗示了逻辑关系。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当 GPT-5.2 强行把图片转成纯文本时，这些“非文字信息”全部丢失了。它看到的只是一堆干巴巴的字符。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;text-align: left;font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\">而 Gemini 3 Pro 因为是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;text-align: left;font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">原生多模态</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;text-align: left;font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\">，像素和字符在它的神经网络里是平权的。它能同时看到“字的意思”和“字的样子”。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对独立开发者的启示</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为产品人，我们必须敏锐地捕捉到这种技术代差带来的机会。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前我们做“文档对话”、“AI 辅导”这类产品，不得不忍受 OCR 的高昂成本和慢速响应。用户上传一个 PDF，得转圈半天。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Pro 把这个链路打通了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着我们可以构建</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">完全实时</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的视觉交互产品。用户拍一张复杂的报表，AI 毫秒级给出分析结果——这种体验的提升，是 10 倍级的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">时延的消失，往往意味着新交互形态的诞生。</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;margin: 35px 0px 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(211, 47, 47);color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">留个作业</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我知道我的读者里有很多卧虎藏龙的开发者和超级个体。Gemini 3 Pro 的这个特性，绝对不止是用来做题这么简单。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能看懂1小时的无字幕电影、截图出里面最精彩的金句帧吗？</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能直接看一个抖音卖货视频，逐秒分析出视频脚本、找出视频的亮点吗？</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能把抖音特效运镜视频逆向成图生视频的Prompt吗？</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能直接看懂你复杂的 Figma 设计稿并写出代码吗？（不需要切图）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能看懂股票 K 线图的走势形态吗？</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">别光听我说，去试。把你手头最复杂的、最让 OCR 头疼的文件丢给它。如果你发现了什么惊人的原生多模态用法，在评论区告诉我。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">咱们评论区见，期待你的反馈！期待你告诉我更多！</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章通过对比测试，揭示了 Gemini 3 Pro 与 GPT-5.2 在多模态理解能力上的代差，强调原生多模态对信息处理效率和产品创新的重大意义。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章通过对比测试，揭示了 Gemini 3 Pro 与 GPT-5.2 在多模态理解能力上的代差，强调原生多模态对信息处理效率和产品创新的重大意义。",
  "summary": "作者通过一个极端的多模态测试场景（一本数百页的扫描版教材和 200 道带图表的题目），对比了 GPT-5.2 和 Gemini 3 Pro 的表现。结果显示，GPT-5.2 采用“OCR+胶水”模式，耗时 20 多分钟才处理部分内容，并出现信息熵丢失；而 Gemini 3 Pro 则以原生多模态方式，在 1 分钟内准确完成所有题目，体现出更强的视觉理解能力。文章强调真正的多模态应是原生理解而非管道式拼接，并指出这种技术代差将为独立开发者带来实时视觉交互产品创新的巨大机会。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GPT-5.2 的多模态能力本质是“OCR+LLM”的胶水模式，效率低下且存在信息熵丢失。",
      "explanation": "GPT-5.2 通过调用 Python Sandbox 和 OCR 库将图片转文字再处理，耗时巨大，并丢失了图片中文字大小、图表颜色、布局等非文字信息，无法实现真正的视觉理解。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Pro 展现了原生多模态的强大能力，能够直接理解视觉信息，实现高效和精确处理。",
      "explanation": "Gemini 3 Pro 无需中间转换，能直接“看懂”扫描版教材，在极短时间内完成复杂任务，其神经网络能同时处理像素和字符，体现了更高级的视觉认知能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "原生多模态的技术代差将催生新的交互形态和产品创新机会。",
      "explanation": "时延的消失和实时视觉处理能力，使得开发者能够构建完全实时的视觉交互产品，例如毫秒级分析复杂报表，将带来 10 倍级用户体验提升和产品创新潜力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
